  <brief_title>The Safety and Efficacy of Basiliximab as Maintenance Therapy in Subjects With Stable, Noninfectious Uveitis</brief_title>
  <acronym>BSX-003</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-Masked, Placebo-controlled Evaluation of the Safety and Efficacy of Basiliximab as Maintenance Therapy in Subjects With Stable, Noninfectious Uveitis Who Undergo Tapering of Concomitant Immunosuppressive Medications</official_title>
